{"tid":1666851,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中學教材稱黃之鋒為中華傳統美德名人    外交部怒斥","createTime":"2019-10-21T07:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T08:05:33.000Z","uid":65371,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"904afb2bcc7eb542d355becf8603121d3ba1af37","tid":1666851,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/973458336362308/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393304404377707%2Fposts%2F973458336362308%2F&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=931c6054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393304404377707/posts/973458336362308/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fV3MvR1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfV3MvR1.jpg&h=1831e73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港某中學教材稱黃之鋒為「中華傳統美德名人」引發怒斥】<br />\n<br />\n據香港媒體報道，根據社交媒體近日流傳的一張圖片<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">，香港某中學教材將「港獨」分子黃之鋒奉為「中華傳統美德名人」，稱其組織「反國民教育」示威遊行，表現出「過人的口才和應對」、「獲市民大讚」、「備受矚目」云云</span></span>。該教材更將黃煽動人「包圍政府總部」、違法「佔中」等劣行當成將其奉為「中華傳統美德名人」的論據，行文間更不乏抹黑中央政府的言論。<br />\n<br />\n香港教評會主席何漢權批評此舉完全是對中華文化的極大扭曲。他表示，如果把黃作為一個負面人物、負面教材，反而可以接受。<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港教育政策關注社主席張民炳表示，對於某些學校的內部教材出現問題，希望香港教育局去監管，不能讓偏頗政治訊息誤導莘莘學子。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國務院港澳事務辦公室發言人徐露穎曾指出，香港的國民教育確實存在缺失。一些亂港分子、禍港分子，為政治圖謀利用年輕人充當棋子、炮灰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Ar2rWFEo-vNdBose9Ri4Pg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FAr2rWFEo-vNdBose9Ri4Pg&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=931d5441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Ar2rWFEo-vNdBose9Ri4Pg</a><br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n歡迎關注公署官方微信公眾號(帳號:fmcoprc)，希望為你提供豐富有益的資訊和便捷周到的服務。"},{"pid":"7d57de3ae34badd375d70c7f985ee3f24a9f433a","tid":1666851,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"f017b54810bc80eab2e42d0610d6ef7777624891","tid":1666851,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435686ff59f71f81a0324f3d6db384562c7cda6a","tid":1666851,"uid":34525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:13:40.000Z","msg":"又關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855dc60348eb6435b9ad2b5d64ed652aaa3433b2","tid":1666851,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"h"},{"pid":"6c1e43ef55df025e653f3508dae99b8b967d35c2","tid":1666851,"uid":301906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"又係何漢權 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ba8832e38703e13224cb01521dd6cc91bc44d8","tid":1666851,"uid":112198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"玻璃心又碎"},{"pid":"e99ddc0c569bf9656929b58ab7c2754a2c00b021","tid":1666851,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"0e573a77ccd7352bcea2b194afcc645e9047c6d1","tid":1666851,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00d7eb43e3b134ba2aa1664bb9620028d41b132","tid":1666851,"uid":88366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"支持民主又真係唔係中國人美德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067a1165e1f8c309212740df043aa61a57d66f04","tid":1666851,"uid":39098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00d7eb43e3b134ba2aa1664bb9620028d41b132","tid":1666851,"uid":88366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"支持民主又真係唔係中國人美德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"仁義禮智"},{"pid":"fa33d02f80530350f58aadb98b770f7d7ebdb8f8","tid":1666851,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d038ccee9f5dd5f9d6ca4405dda4e7ec879c81","tid":1666851,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349564860dbc9eac80c5b30992253418001cdf3d","tid":1666851,"uid":304512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T08:05:33.000Z","msg":"雖然我覺得ghone未必係「傳統美德名人」，但對家共媒，你就收皮啦，關你X事？"}]}